---
import ronaldImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/Reviews/RonaldRichards.png?url';
import floydImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/Reviews/FloydMiles.png?url';
import darrellImg from '../../../assets/Images/HomePageImg/Reviews/DarrellSteward.png?url';
import likeIcon from '../../../assets/Icons/ReUseableIcons/ReviewsIcons/like.png';
---

<section class="seventh-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Trusted by Thousands of Homeowners</h2>
            <p>Real experiences from families who chose our invisible grills to<br>protect their homes without compromising on design.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card card-top">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">I will let my mum know about this, she could really make use of software! Very easy to use. Since I invested in software I made over 100,000 dollars profits. I just can't get enough of software. I want to get a T-Shirt with software on it so I can show it off to everyone.</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <div class="author-image">
                        <img src={ronaldImg} alt="Ronald Richards" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <div class="author-name">Ronald Richards</div>
                        <div class="author-role">Gillette</div>
                        <div class="badge"><img src={likeIcon.src} alt="Reviews" class="like-icon" /> Testimonial</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial-card card-bottom">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">I can't say enough about software. I will refer everyone I know. After using software my business skyrocketed! Not able to tell you how happy I am with software.</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <div class="author-image">
                        <img src={floydImg} alt="Floyd Miles" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <div class="author-name">Floyd Miles</div>
                        <div class="author-role">Louis Vuitton</div>
                        <div class="badge"><img src={likeIcon.src} alt="Reviews" class="like-icon" /> Testimonial</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial-card card-top">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">I like Infinity Estate more and more each day because it makes my life a lot easier. We can't understand how we've been living without Infinity Estate. Infinity Estate has got everything I need. The service was excellent.</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <div class="author-image">
                        <img src={darrellImg} alt="Darrell Steward" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <div class="author-name">Darrell Steward</div>
                        <div class="author-role">Ferrari</div>
                        <div class="badge"><img src={likeIcon.src} alt="Reviews" class="like-icon" /> Testimonial</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .seventh-section {
        width: 100%;
        background: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 100px 0 120px 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 1100px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .header h2 {
        font-family: 'Montaga', serif;
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .header p {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #666;
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 80px;
        align-items: end; /* Align cards to the bottom */
    }

    .testimonial-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 40px 20px 20px 20px; /* top-left, top-right, bottom-right, bottom-left */
        padding: 25px 30px; /* Reduced padding */
        position: relative;
        box-shadow: 12px 12px 0px #B37A42; /* Updated shadow color */
        border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        height: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    /* Height variations */
    .testimonial-card:nth-child(1) {
        min-height: 350px; /* Tallest */
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .testimonial-card:nth-child(2) {
        min-height: 260px; /* Shortest */
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .testimonial-card:nth-child(3) {
        min-height: 305px; /* Middle height */
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .card-top, .card-bottom {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .stars {
        color: #B37A42;
        font-size: 16px; /* Reduced */
        margin-bottom: 12px; /* Reduced */
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-left: 70px; /* Align with author info */
    }

    .testimonial-text {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px; /* Reduced */
        line-height: 1.5; /* Reduced */
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Reduced */
        flex-grow: 1;
        margin-left: 70px; /* Align with author info */
    }

    .author {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center; /* Remove gap as image is absolute */
        position: static; /* Ensure author container doesn't trap absolute if we want card relative, but card is relative so this is fine */
        margin-top: auto; /* Push to bottom if needed, though split-between does it */
    }

    .author-image {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        overflow: hidden;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        background: #ddd;
        position: absolute;
        left: -60px; /* Half outside (120/2) */
        bottom: 0px; /* Aligned with bottom edge */
        border: 4px solid white; /* Add border for separation */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .author-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .author-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2px;
        margin-left: 70px; /* Space for half the image (60px visible) + some padding */
    }

    .author-name {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #333;
    }

    .author-role {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
    }

    .badge {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #202020;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4px;
    }

    .like-icon {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }
</style>


